    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include documented preventative maintenance on the VANOS system and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing a refined MacPherson strut and multi-link setup for exceptional lateral grip. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle presents as a mechanically robust specimen with a documented service history, ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
