    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained Graphite Metallic sedan that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. This vehicle has served as a dependable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical health. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor rock chips on the front fascia and a three-inch superficial scratch near the rear passenger wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has seen the road but has been loved. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium black leather upholstery that remains supple and free of any rips or significant bolster wear. All electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises; the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. I have kept a comprehensive log of all services, including a recent brake pad replacement and a fresh synthetic oil change performed just 500 miles ago. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, providing plenty of grip for the seasons ahead. This is a complete, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
